Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.42,0:01:36.76,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}(Dream save us us) a-su, All of us{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.76,0:01:46.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The Straw Hats that got separated from\NLuffy, Chopper, and Jimbei...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.35,0:01:50.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...came across an unexpected party.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.19,0:01:57.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm only a genius scientist\Nworking for the Government!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.07,0:02:03.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Dr. Vegapunk!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.34,0:02:20.97,Default,,0,0,0,,What is all this stuff?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.97,0:02:31.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Meanwhile, Luffy and the others\Nwere exploring the Future Island Egghead.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.77,0:02:33.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And they ran into...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.73,0:02:36.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You bastards don't look familiar to me...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.08,0:02:45.41,Default,,0,0,0,,A girl?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.54,0:02:47.12,Default,,0,0,0,,More than anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.33,0:02:53.59,Default,,0,0,0,,She's huge!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.71,0:02:55.13,Default,,0,0,0,,What's with that child?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.25,0:02:57.09,Default,,0,0,0,,She's bigger than Kaido.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.21,0:03:00.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Who in the world are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.93,0:03:04.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.43,0:03:07.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm only a genius scientist for hire!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.44,0:03:15.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Vegapunk!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.90,0:03:19.44,On Top,,0,0,0,,VIOLENCE (ATLAS)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.57,0:03:21.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You're Dr. Vegapunk?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.86,0:03:25.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Koby told me about you!\NYou're too big and too young!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.28,0:03:28.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No way! What is she talking about?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.29,0:03:37.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"Bonney's Lamentation!\NDarkness Lurking on the Future Island"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.75,0:03:40.59,On Top,,0,0,0,,NEW WORLD
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.59,0:03:46.01,Default,,0,0,0,,So what should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.14,0:03:49.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen carefully.\NThere's only one Vegapunk.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.52,0:03:54.56,Default,,0,0,0,,That's stating the obvious.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.11,0:03:57.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't interrupt.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.44,0:03:59.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.57,0:04:03.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen.\NThere's only one Vegapunk in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.78,0:04:05.99,Default,,0,0,0,,But he's so busy because he's such a genius.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.58,0:04:10.20,Default,,0,0,0,,He doesn't have enough time.\NHe'll take all the help he can get.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.83,0:04:12.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Then he came up with an idea...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.50,0:04:16.25,Default,,0,0,0,,...to split himself into six.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.71,0:04:21.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Those offshoots are called Satellites.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.34,0:04:21.84,On Top,,0,0,0,,YORK ATLAS PYTHAGORAS EDISON LILITH SHAKA
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.97,0:04:24.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Punk-01, Shaka!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.01,0:04:24.80,On Top,,0,0,0,,SHAKA (GOOD)
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.93,0:04:27.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Punk-02, Lilith!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.97,0:04:27.76,On Top,,0,0,0,,LILITH (EVIL)
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.89,0:04:30.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Punk-03, Edison!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.93,0:04:30.72,On Top,,0,0,0,,EDISON (THINKER)
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.85,0:04:33.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Punk-04, Pythagoras!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.89,0:04:33.69,On Top,,0,0,0,,PYTHAGORAS (WISDOM)
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.81,0:04:36.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Punk-05, Atlas!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.85,0:04:36.65,On Top,,0,0,0,,ATLAS (VIOLENCE)
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.77,0:04:39.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Punk-06, York!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.82,0:04:39.61,On Top,,0,0,0,,YORK (GREED)
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.73,0:04:44.03,On Top,,0,0,0,,YORK ATLAS PYTHAGORAS EDISON LILITH SHAKA
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.15,0:04:43.07,Default,,0,0,0,,In other words, these six Satellites...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.11,0:04:45.61,Default,,0,0,0,,...are all Vegapunk!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.74,0:04:45.61,On Top,,0,0,0,,VEGAPUNK
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.74,0:04:49.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Am I crazy to think that can't be true?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.04,0:04:55.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Being a genius is a pain...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.37,0:04:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,His "cats" are quite troublesome, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.30,0:05:02.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Just like their owner.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.59,0:05:09.47,Default,,0,0,0,,So our mission is...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.51,0:05:11.68,Default,,0,0,0,,...to return this bastard to Egghead,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.72,0:05:15.14,On Top,,0,0,0,,CIPHER POL "AIGIS" ZERO\N(MASKED ASSASSINS) KAKU, LUCCI, STUSSY
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.72,0:05:14.85,Default,,0,0,0,,and eliminate all the Vegapunks.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.98,0:05:17.31,Default,,0,0,0,,The lab is full of valuable stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.35,0:05:19.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Be careful with those while you're at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.23,0:05:23.61,Default,,0,0,0,,We will eliminate the handiest man\Nin the world...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.20,0:05:30.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Does this have something to do with\Nwhat happened to Lulusia the other day?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.03,0:05:33.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be nosy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.16,0:05:36.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Not when your intuition is as good as yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.00,0:05:38.58,Default,,0,0,0,,She's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.63,0:05:41.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't get us involved, Lucci!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.77,0:06:04.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You're that well-known Vegapunk?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.32,0:06:05.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I am!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.99,0:06:09.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never heard\Nthat Vegapunk was a child...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.28,0:06:12.12,Default,,0,0,0,,And so huge...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.58,0:06:17.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you guys satisfied?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.21,0:06:19.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it was so good.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.92,0:06:23.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone will be surprised\Nwhen they see the food machine.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.75,0:06:28.05,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a shame that they aren't here yet\Nto see such a great thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.17,0:06:30.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, maybe Sanji will get mad.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.84,0:06:35.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys ate so much!\NAll your stomachs are about to burst!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.68,0:06:37.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Mine's always been like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.06,0:06:41.48,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.61,0:06:43.65,Default,,0,0,0,,That's Recycollie.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.69,0:06:47.19,Default,,0,0,0,,It consumes and breaks down garbage\Nand reconstitutes it to be a resource.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.24,0:06:48.36,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so brilliant!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.61,0:06:51.70,On Top,,0,0,0,,RECYCOLLIE
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.82,0:06:54.12,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's like its food.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.24,0:06:55.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.62,0:06:57.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Here's your food. Eat it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.34,0:07:11.22,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.97,0:07:20.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Go away! I feel heavy!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.06,0:07:23.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Why am I being chased too?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.06,0:07:26.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Luffy's the one who did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.19,0:07:33.82,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way,\NRecycollie won't tolerate littering.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.95,0:07:35.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You should've told me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.05,0:07:51.38,Default,,0,0,0,,They are so funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.97,0:07:53.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to throw garbage into a trash can.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.01,0:07:56.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes... I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.02,0:08:02.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I gotta go now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.89,0:08:04.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you leaving already?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.56,0:08:06.61,Default,,0,0,0,,My job is to be violent.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.73,0:08:08.07,Default,,0,0,0,,What kind of job is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.19,0:08:10.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for the food!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.40,0:08:13.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Enjoy your stay on Egghead.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.93,0:08:39.43,Default,,0,0,0,,What are they?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.10,0:08:42.10,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a lab so...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.14,0:08:43.89,Default,,0,0,0,,...I think they're researchers.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.02,0:08:47.36,Default,,0,0,0,,There wasn't anybody in the town,\Nbut now I see some people...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.40,0:08:51.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe they were taking precautions\Nagainst us.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.61,0:08:55.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Their outfits look heavy\Neven though this is a tropical island.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.95,0:08:56.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.57,0:08:58.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's Luffy?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.08,0:09:05.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this also a food machine?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.92,0:09:10.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Welcome. Choose the clothes you like.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.30,0:09:13.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd rather have food.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.51,0:09:15.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, well!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.43,0:09:17.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Here we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.85,0:09:21.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Are there any other requests?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.35,0:09:24.89,Default,,0,0,0,,This and this and this...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.93,0:09:26.73,Default,,0,0,0,,And this!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.40,0:09:35.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! It's moving!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.45,0:09:45.66,Default,,0,0,0,,W-What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.63,0:09:50.84,Default,,0,0,0,,That's Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.96,0:09:53.63,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.67,0:09:55.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't take the hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.34,0:09:57.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.72,0:09:59.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Is he in there?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.76,0:10:03.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.85,0:10:06.02,Default,,0,0,0,,How do I look?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.64,0:10:09.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I love it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.28,0:10:16.36,Default,,0,0,0,,How funny!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.95,0:10:18.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't it heavy?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.66,0:10:20.37,Default,,0,0,0,,It's really light!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.41,0:10:22.70,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's cooler inside!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.20,0:10:24.87,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fashionable.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.99,0:10:26.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanna wear it, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.29,0:10:27.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Where did you get it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.33,0:10:29.17,Default,,0,0,0,,This!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.29,0:10:31.46,Default,,0,0,0,,They're giving us food and clothes!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.58,0:10:33.46,Default,,0,0,0,,This island is awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.59,0:10:36.38,Default,,0,0,0,,To be honest,\NI feel sticky because of the seawater!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.51,0:10:39.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Choose the clothes you like.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.84,0:10:40.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I like?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.97,0:10:43.51,Default,,0,0,0,,A combat dress!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.22,0:10:46.06,Default,,0,0,0,,A cool one!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.18,0:10:48.39,Default,,0,0,0,,This looks light.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.90,0:10:55.28,Default,,0,0,0,,It's really high-tech!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.91,0:11:11.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I can take them off myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.84,0:11:20.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.43,0:11:24.30,Default,,0,0,0,,They're really light!\NI feel like I'm floating with these shoes!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.35,0:11:25.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.89,0:11:27.85,Default,,0,0,0,,The future!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.31,0:11:30.44,Default,,0,0,0,,There was a tropical style one, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.56,0:11:32.85,Default,,0,0,0,,That looks good on you, Jimbei!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.98,0:11:36.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah? It's just right for a disguise.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.27,0:11:38.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe it's too late though...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.03,0:11:46.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't forget that you're intruders.\NBe careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.83,0:11:51.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go find a weapon\Nand track down Vegapunk.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.71,0:11:52.62,Default,,0,0,0,,So bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.75,0:11:54.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You must be careful, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.75,0:11:56.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.43,0:12:06.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.35,0:12:08.35,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.77,0:12:10.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Did something happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.56,0:12:15.23,Default,,0,0,0,,That's Kuma!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.36,0:12:16.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Kuma?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.08,0:12:36.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Is he looking for us?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.91,0:13:52.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it just my imagination?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.37,0:13:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's run!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.33,0:14:00.04,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.50,0:14:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,He's gonna run!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.09,0:14:04.46,Default,,0,0,0,,He's targeting us!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.59,0:14:05.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.43,0:14:11.68,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?! Explain it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.80,0:14:13.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Just keep running!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.64,0:14:15.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.90,0:14:28.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Dine and dash! Stealing clothes!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.78,0:14:33.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Here comes the laser cannon!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.58,0:14:44.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't know I needed to pay!\NIt came out when I kicked it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.38,0:14:46.05,Default,,0,0,0,,That's vandalism.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.35,0:14:54.93,Default,,0,0,0,,They'd kill us over an eat and run?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.06,0:14:56.56,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a little too harsh.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.10,0:15:03.65,Default,,0,0,0,,If we don't fight back,\Nwe'll be in danger!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.77,0:15:07.40,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a form of self-defense\Nif we put aside the fact that we're pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.53,0:15:10.32,Default,,0,0,0,,All right! I feel bad, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.97,0:15:32.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.39,0:15:41.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.70,0:15:54.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Why did you do that, Bonney?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.82,0:15:58.04,Default,,0,0,0,,He's using laser beams!\NWhy can't I at least punch...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.89,0:16:16.39,Default,,0,0,0,,He's my father...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.89,0:16:21.60,Default,,0,0,0,,The only...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.94,0:16:26.77,Default,,0,0,0,,...family I have left!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.90,0:16:28.48,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.53,0:16:36.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Your father who was turned into a cyborg...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.28,0:16:38.33,Default,,0,0,0,,...is Kuma?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.22,0:16:59.18,Default,,0,0,0,,So please!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.22,0:17:01.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't hurt my father!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.39,0:17:03.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Idiot! Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.10,0:17:05.31,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a Pacifista!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.65,0:17:09.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Bonney!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.86,0:17:11.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Bonney!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.24,0:17:19.70,On Top,,0,0,0,,A CERTAIN SEA AREA, NEW WORLD
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.83,0:17:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It's nice and sunny!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.54,0:17:24.87,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a lovely day!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.33,0:17:27.96,Default,,0,0,0,,So peaceful!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.71,0:17:30.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Bepo, do your job!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.00,0:17:33.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You're on cleaning duty, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.26,0:17:37.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I've already finished cleaning\Nthe area that I'm in charge of!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.05,0:17:39.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sunbathing now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.14,0:17:41.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Because you're rolling around there...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.56,0:17:44.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Our work will never be done!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.52,0:17:47.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at this! This is all your hair!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.69,0:17:49.86,Default,,0,0,0,,There is hair all over the deck!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.61,0:17:52.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it shedding season?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.23,0:17:55.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you guys lose your hair?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.28,0:17:57.53,Default,,0,0,0,,We'd be shocked if we lost this much!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.66,0:18:00.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you just shut up and help us?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.24,0:18:01.91,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.21,0:18:15.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Here they come.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.92,0:18:17.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Our prey!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.94,0:18:34.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Brace your nerves, guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.12,0:18:52.84,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter what happens from here on,\Nthere's no way we're running away!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.00,0:18:56.55,Default,,0,0,0,,While we fight pirates like them...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.86,0:19:21.61,Default,,0,0,0,,We're gonna just keep going!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.17,0:19:32.92,On Top,,0,0,0,,JESUS BURGESS (STRONG-STRONG FRUIT)
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.55,0:19:40.26,On Top,,0,0,0,,VAN OGRE (WARP-WARP FRUIT)
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.59,0:19:45.26,On Top,,0,0,0,,STRONGER (HORSE-HORSE FRUIT,\NMYTHICAL TYPE, MODEL: PEGASUS)
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.60,0:19:47.18,On Top,,0,0,0,,DOC Q (SICK-SICK FRUIT)
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.85,0:19:54.98,On Top,,0,0,0,,EMPEROR OF THE SEA, BLACKBEARD\NMARSHALL D. TEECH, BOUNTY: 3.996 BILLION BERRIES
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.65,0:19:56.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.73,0:20:00.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's get this party started!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.32,0:20:05.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go, guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.04,0:20:21.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}How far I have run{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.04,0:20:21.17,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}doredake hashitte kita noka{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.88,0:20:28.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Without knowing it, I counted scars{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.88,0:20:28.47,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}wakaranai mama kizuato kazoeta{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.93,0:20:35.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A treasure map in my head all along{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.93,0:20:35.90,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}zutto atama no naka ni aru takara no chizu{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.94,0:20:42.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Still looking for the future{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.94,0:20:42.40,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}mirai wo sagashi tsuzuketeru{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.45,0:20:49.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The real promise{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.45,0:20:49.12,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}hontou no yakusoku wa{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.16,0:20:56.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Lies much deeper in my heart{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.16,0:20:56.29,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}mune no oku no motto oku ni aru{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.33,0:21:05.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A dream that no one can catch up with{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.33,0:21:05.43,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}dare mo mina oitsukenai yume{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.47,0:21:11.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's all I hold on to{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.47,0:21:11.14,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}tada hitotsu dakishimete{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.18,0:21:18.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}To you who smiles like the sun{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.18,0:21:18.23,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}taiyou no youni warau anata e{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.27,0:21:25.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll sing the same song as that day{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.27,0:21:25.15,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}ano hi to onaji uta wo utau yo{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.20,0:21:32.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This wish I don't want to forget even when I grow up{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.20,0:21:32.20,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}otona ni nattemo wasuretakunai{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.24,0:21:39.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Until it reaches you{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.24,0:21:39.67,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}kono negai ga todoku made{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.47,0:21:50.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"Tell Me, Robin!\NChopper's I-Wanna-Learn-More-You-Fool!"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.43,0:21:55.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, guys! I'm Chopper,\Nthe ship's doctor of the Straw Hats!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.68,0:21:57.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Robin, an archaeologist.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.52,0:21:59.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Robin, I can't wait to learn as always!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.44,0:22:04.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Information can be a strong weapon.\NLet's keep learning!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.40,0:22:08.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Today we'll learn about this one!\NRob Lucci!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.49,0:22:12.62,Default,,0,0,0,,He's an agent of Cipher Pol, an intelligence organization\Nworking directly under the World Government.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.66,0:22:16.66,Default,,0,0,0,,He uses Six Powers, martial arts\Nthat turn a well-trained body into a weapon.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.08,0:22:20.38,Default,,0,0,0,,He was born on June 2nd\Nand he likes brandy.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.42,0:22:26.63,Default,,0,0,0,,He's also a user of the Zoan type Devil Fruit,\NCat-Cat Fruit, Leopard Model.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.76,0:22:29.64,Default,,0,0,0,,We first met him in Water Seven.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.68,0:22:32.72,Default,,0,0,0,,To obtain the blueprints for\NPluton, the Ancient Weapon,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.76,0:22:38.06,Default,,0,0,0,,he was working for the Galley-La Company\Nfor five years, hiding that he was a CP9 agent.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.69,0:22:40.81,Default,,0,0,0,,After he and the others\Nrevealed their true identities,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.86,0:22:45.48,Default,,0,0,0,,they took Robin away\Nto Enies Lobby, the World Government's island.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.99,0:22:47.90,Default,,0,0,0,,In the name of dark justice!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.03,0:22:52.49,Default,,0,0,0,,If you guys didn't come then,\NI wouldn't be where I am today.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.62,0:22:56.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Luffy busted Lucci\Nand we were able to take Robin back!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.87,0:23:01.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like he is an agent of Cipher Pol "Aigis" Zero\Nwhich is working directly under the World Nobles.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.00,0:23:05.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder why\Nhe has a pigeon on his shoulder.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.67,0:23:10.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Egghead is becoming even more chaotic.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.43,0:23:13.35,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it for this week! See you next time!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.47,0:23:14.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.77,0:23:25.15,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll feature our captain, the leader\Nof the Heart Pirates, Trafalgar Law!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.27,0:23:27.57,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll look back on his life!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.69,0:23:32.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Make sure to tune in to get a taste\Nof our captain's awesomeness!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.28,0:23:33.74,Default,,0,0,0,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.28,0:23:39.20,Default,,0,0,0,,"A Project to Fully Enjoy!\N'Surgeon of Death' Trafalgar Law"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.33,0:23:45.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Our captain is the King of the Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.71,0:23:47.71,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.71,0:23:49.71,On Top,,0,0,0,,
